## Request-Response Flow Pattern

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as React Frontend
    participant API as API Route
    participant Auth as requireAuth()
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>UI: Click button
    UI->>API: POST /api/endpoint

    API->>Auth: requireAuth(['role'])
    Auth->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE clerkUserId = ?
    DB-->>Auth: User data
    Auth-->>API: { userId, user }

    API->>DB: Execute query
    DB-->>API: Result data

    API->>API: Process data
    API->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE

    DB-->>API: Success
    API-->>UI: { success: true, data }
    UI-->>User: Show success message
```

