## 8. Leave Request & Approval Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "REQUEST FLOW"
        A[Student/Teacher] --> B[Click Request Leave]
        B --> C[FeatureForm: LeaveFeature]
        C --> D[Fill: type, dates, reason]
        D --> E[POST /api/leave]

        E --> F[Validate leave balance]
        F --> G{Balance sufficient?}
        G -->|No| H[Return error: Insufficient leave]
        G -->|Yes| I[CREATE leave_requests<br/>status: pending]

        I --> J[Return success]
        J --> K[Show pending status]
    end

    subgraph "APPROVAL FLOW"
        L[School Admin] --> M[GET /api/leave?status=pending]
        M --> N[Display pending requests]

        N --> O{Admin Action}
        O -->|Approve| P[PATCH /api/leave/[id]<br/>action: approve]
        O -->|Reject| Q[PATCH /api/leave/[id]<br/>action: reject]

        P --> R[Update status: approved<br/>Set approvedBy, approvedAt<br/>Set substitute if provided]
        Q --> S[Update status: rejected<br/>Set rejectionReason]

        R --> T[Notify applicant]
        S --> T
        T --> U[Update dashboard]
    end

    subgraph "CANCEL FLOW"
        V[Applicant] --> W[PATCH /api/leave/[id]<br/>action: cancel]
        W --> X{Status = pending?}
        X -->|No| Y[Return error: Cannot cancel]
        X -->|Yes| Z[Update status: cancelled]
        Z --> AA[Return success]
    end

    style C fill:#e1f5ff
    style I fill:#d4edda
    style R fill:#d4edda
    style S fill:#f8d7da
    style Y fill:#f8d7da
    style Z fill:#fff3cd
```

**API Endpoints:**
- `GET /api/leave` - List requests (filtered by role)
- `POST /api/leave` - Create request
- `PATCH /api/leave/[id]` - Approve/Reject/Cancel
- `DELETE /api/leave/[id]` - Delete (pending/rejected only)

**Database Tables:**
1. `leave_requests` - Request records
2. `users` - Applicant and approver linkage

**Leave Types:**
- sick, vacation, emergency, family, casual, official, other

