## 10. Student Skills & Learning Path Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "SKILL COLLECTION"
        A[Student] --> B{Skill Source}
        B -->|Self-Report| C[POST /api/student/skills/self-report]
        B -->|AI Inferred| D[POST /api/student/skills/inferred]

        C --> E["CREATE student_skills<br/>{ studentId, skillId, level: 'beginner', source: 'self' }"]
        D --> F["CREATE student_skills<br/>{ studentId, skillId, level: 'intermediate', source: 'ai' }"]

        E --> G[Return skill record]
        F --> G
    end

    subgraph "LEARNING PATH GENERATION"
        G --> H[GET /api/student/learning-path]
        H --> I[Query student_skills]
        I --> J[Analyze skill gaps]

        J --> K[Cross-reference modules]
        K --> L["Match: skills → modules.learningObjectives"]

        L --> M[Generate path]
        M --> N["Sort by: dependency order<br/>Filter: not completed"]

        N --> O[Return recommended modules]
    end

    subgraph "CAREER MATCHING"
        O --> P[GET /api/student/career-matches]
        P --> Q[Get student_skills]
        Q --> R[Get academic performance]

        R --> S[Query careers catalog]
        S --> T["Match: career.requiredSkills ∩ student.skills"]

        T --> U[Calculate match score]
        U --> V[Sort by match score]
        V --> W[Return top 10 careers]
    end

    subgraph "MODULE PROGRESS"
        W --> X[Student starts module]
        X --> Y[POST /api/student/modules/[id]/progress]
        Y --> Z["CREATE/UPDATE module_progress<br/>{ studentId, moduleId, progress: 25 }"]

        Z --> AA{Progress = 100%?}
        AA -->|Yes| AB[POST /api/student/modules/[id]/complete]
        AA -->|No| AC[Continue module]

        AB --> AD["UPDATE module_progress.status: 'completed'<br/>SET completedAt"]
        AD --> AE[GET /api/student/modules/[id]/certificate]
        AE --> AF[Generate certificate PDF]
    end

    style E fill:#d4edda
    style M fill:#fff3c7
    style U fill:#e1f5ff
    style AD fill:#c3e6cb
    style AF fill:#a7f3d0
```

**API Endpoints:**
- `POST /api/student/skills/self-report` - Add self-reported skill
- `POST /api/student/skills/inferred` - Add AI-inferred skill
- `GET /api/student/learning-path` - Get learning path
- `GET /api/student/career-matches` - Get career matches
- `POST /api/student/modules/[id]/progress` - Update progress
- `POST /api/student/modules/[id]/complete` - Mark complete
- `GET /api/student/modules/[id]/certificate` - Get certificate
- `GET /api/student/modules/recommendations` - Get recommendations

**Database Tables:**
1. `student_skills` - Skill records
2. `skills` - Skill catalog
3. `modules` - Learning modules
4. `module_progress` - Progress tracking
5. `careers` - Career catalog
6. `career_matches` - Match results

