## 13. Unified API Request Flow (v3.0)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant R as Router
    participant CR as createApiRoute
    participant AU as requireAuth
    participant F as Feature Handler
    participant DB as Database

    C->>R: GET /api/resources/users
    R->>CR: Invoke handler

    CR->>AU: await requireAuth(request)
    AU->>DB: SELECT user BY clerkUserId
    DB-->>AU: User data
    AU-->>CR: { userId, user }

    CR->>CR: Check allowedRoles
    CR->>F: Feature.handlers.list(params)

    F->>DB: SELECT with relations
    DB-->>F: Results

    F->>F: Transform & format
    F-->>CR: Processed data

    CR->>CR: successResponse(data)
    CR-->>C: JSON { success: true, data }
```

